[[File:Yosef Gorny cropped.jpg|thumb|upright|Gorny (June 2008)]]
'''Yosef Gorny''' ([[Hebrew]]: יוסף גורני) (born 1933), is  Professor of Study of Zionism and head of the Zionist Research Institute at the [[Tel Aviv University]].<ref>[http://www.tau.ac.il/humanities/faculty/gorni.htm Prof. Yosef Gorny, Head, Zionist Research Institute] {{webarchive |url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060117182138/http://www.tau.ac.il/humanities/faculty/gorni.htm |date=January 17, 2006 }}</ref> He is a former head of the [[Weizmann Institute]] for the Study of Zionism, at the same university.

